  # GUS4_STATUS | RAD.SageTag                    | auto   | absent
  # GUS4_STATUS | RAD.Analysis                   | auto   | absent
  # GUS4_STATUS | ApiDB.Profile                  | auto   | absent
  # GUS4_STATUS | Study.Study                    | auto   | absent
